| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5800 — Recovery Inhibition (babuk2)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 263aa52f-9fb3-55a9-a9f6-10013aef76ad"
